Text: They go to separate courts, and the games begin.
*gasp*!
Woooah!
At the height of her jump, Delta glares at Zeta.
Take this, you filthy alley cat!!!
Delta spikes the ball at breakneck speed toward Zeta.
Zeta evades as if she saw it coming,
and uses her tail to deflect the ball toward the net.
Wha-?!
Skel?!
Skeeel?!
Why...
Hey, it's your fault with that crazy pass.
It's your fault for dodging it, kitty cat.

I didn't dodge it, I hit it back like I was supposed
to.
Using your tail is against the rules!

Oh, you actually learned the rules! What a good dumb
doggie.
Who you calling dumb, furball?!
*sigh*...
Honestly...what are they doing?
I knew I should have been chosen to go.
This is good.

Everyone looks like they're having a good time.
I don't remember when was the last time we
were able to just have fun.
But, what about the mission from Master Shadow?
What if this is the mission?
Huh?

We've been in constant battle without rest.
We had to, for the world's sake...
—But we were always tense and had no time to unwind.
I think he gave us some much needed time to relax.
Master Shadow...

It's just a guess though. I just thought it might be
a possibility.
I never know what he's thinking...
Hmm...
Is there a problem?

Other than the fact that Nu is opportunistically
using her paid vacation time, there's no—
There is.
Gyah!
Eta.
I sensed a magical reaction a moment ago.
Deep beneath the ground...

The only thing I remember is that we were invited to
play beach volleyball.
Heh, I don't have a clue what happened.
Where are the girls?
I think they're in the women's bath...
Women's bath? Isn't it supposed to be coed?

To cater to various needs, Mitsugoshi Hot Spring Land
is fully equipped with private family baths, children-
only baths, and even separate men and women baths
with no swimsuit required.
Oh, you sure know a lot about it...

—They come on a date only to go into separate hot
springs. You think they're avoiding us?
Heh...quite the opposite.

According to Baron von Smoothe, "The reason girls get
together separately while on a group date is so they
can talk to each other to make sure they aren't after
the same guy."
So things are heading in the right direction!
Furthermore—
Furthermore?

Baron von Smoothe says, "Since ancient times, if men
and women go into separate hot springs, then...there
is essential etiquette to follow."
*gasp*!
Could this mean?!
Yes, it does—

"Wh-Wha?!"
"Ohhh!"
Could we possibly...
Yep, no doubt.
*whimper*

"We're just playing around!"
"We are just playing around!"

No, Beta, you can't let this happen, or you'll end
up a delicate little elf princess again!
That's exactly what's happening.
Oh well... Treasure hunting is hard work.
Unlike me, you two have a big responsibility... Hehe...

That's enough out of you, mutt. You have to think
seriously about Master's goal...
I'm not a mutt!
Master Shadow's...
What could it be...the "Dragon Tear"?
"Dragon Tear"...
